channel.title: Ekstrak - Looking Back [EP, Electro and Dubstep]
channel.description:
My second EP is here! It is with one of each genre: Electro, Dubstep, Drumstep, And House! 3/4 of the songs are remastered takes from Song I made before! Cool, right? The release will be delayed on Spotify or won’t be on Spotify due to mainly bugs for my uploading app. So, without further ado, hope you enjoy these remastered songs.
https://soundcloud.com/shane-brown-97094682/sets/looking-back
